  • ts-auth-service showed multiple resource anomalies: socket, cpu, diskio, latency-50. diskio had a clear spike (max ~68708 vs p95 ~56837) and several consecutive anomaly minutes for socket and cpu as well. Many auth anomalies started at ~2024-01-24T09:37:00Z; some cpu anomalies first appeared later (~09:47Z).
- Fault identification (consecutive sequences):
  • ts-auth-service diskio and socket anomalies formed consecutive sequences (diskio anomalies at 09:37 onward, socket sequences up to 3 minutes), with diskio showing the most pronounced breach relative to its p95.
  • ts-travel-service anomalies were present but their magnitude relative to thresholds was small (and the travel 'error' KPI was a misleading all-zero case). Longest meaningful sequences for travel KPIs were short (1–3 minutes).
- Trace analysis (incident window):
